headline.print_headline: Limited Review Finds White House Political Office Was Within Law
headline.main: Limited Review Finds White House Political Office Was Within Law

lead_paragraph: A limited review found the White House's political office appears to be operating within the law, a federal oversight agency said amid a congressional probe into whether taxpayer money has been used by the Obama administration for political purposes.
